Description:
Stunning French antique still life painting, nature morte, signed Baumat, 1913.
A very striking, well executed still life painting dating from 1913. It is signed on the bottom left for J Baumat and the year.

A wonderful French still life composition that would add some amazing antique style to your home.

Product name: Lost Baby Sympathy Card - Miscarriage Card - Baby Bereavement Card
Description:
A thoughtfully written sympathy card for those who have suffered a miscarriage or stillbirth.
Our unique bereavement card is intended to offer comfort to friends and family who have lost a baby. It could also be used as a reading at a funeral or memorial service.
It is hard to know what to say at such a difficult time. Poet Joanna Miller created this card after hearing that there were few suitable cards available which acknowledge the loss of a baby, whether through miscarriage or still birth.
The wording is the copyright of Bespoke Verse.
The card is square - the inside is blank for your message. The card is printed on FSC accredited 300gsm card. The quality is beautiful! The envelope is kraft (recycled brown). Card and envelope are presented in a cellophane sleeve and posted in a hard-backed envelope.

Product name: Green Ivy leaf garland 2m with mini led fairy string lights rustic wedding decoration, woodland, enchanted forest
Description:
This is a beautiful Ivy leaf garland, made from artificial ivy leaves in two tones of green.  All along the garland is twisted a copper wire containing tiny mirco LEDs in a warm white colour, which make the garland appear to glow and twinkle.  In low light these look really magical.  Because of the copper wire, they can also be 'moulded' into position quite nicely.
Create that enchanted forest look at your wedding or in a bedroom.  Or use them as a stunning unique Christmas decoration.  They would be fantastic as part of a table centerpiece, just hide the battery pack, no need for plugs! Or they would be lovely hanging in a nursery, or draped over a mirror, or on a mantlepiece - they even come in really handy for subtle lighting when camping. The potential for this is limitless.
Because they are LEDs, they are very safe and don't get hot, and because they are battery operated, you can use them almost anywhere!
LED colour is warm white.  
Each garland is 2 metres long.  Requires 3 x AA batteries which are not included.
The lights will be sent via Royal Mail.  If you require tracked postage, please contact me for a price as this will be more expensive.
All my lights come gift wrapped in tissue paper.
Disclaimer:  As with all electrical items, these lights should not be left on unattended.

Description:
These are English fan translations of the Japanese exclusive RPGs Mother 12 and Mother 3 for the Game Boy Advance. Known in English as the Earthbound series: Earthbound Beginnings/Zero  Earthbound and Earthbound 2.
Mother 3 is completely translated into English and is the latest 1.2 version of the highly regarded and professional quality English translation. Mother 1 is also completely translated into English. The Mother 2 translation is incomplete, it is in progress and has most of the menus and items translated along with some of the beginning of the game. There is no complete English translation of Mother 2 available for GBA.

Brand new high quality cartridges available in original grey and clear bright red. The labels are glossy with precut rounded corners. 
Tested and saving works. Flash memory is used for saving, not a battery. Games only, includes small protective cart cases. Photos are of the actual items. 
Region free and compatible in the following systems: Game Boy Advance, GBA SP, original Nintendo DS, Nintendo DS Lite, and the Game Boy Player for Gamecube. *Mother 3 is not compatible with the Game Boy Micro.
Free shipping to the United States and Canada. Sent next business day (Monday through Friday). Estimated delivery time is 4-9 business days to the US and Canada. Delivery to EU countries in 7-15 business days.

***BEFORE PURCHASING - Please be aware that some of information presented in this PDF is available as a very short, text-only free tutorial (written by me) on www.lampworketc.com. This PDF Tutorial will guide you through creating a "tiger" bead in denim blue - a fun and easy design for any level of lampworker.  If you can pull stringer, you can make this!

This tutorial is intended for all lampwork artists who have an understanding of the safety precautions observed in lampworking. Friendly for all torches!  All supplies in this tutorial are readily available from many online glass vendors.  Lauscha and Effetre glass colors are used. I recommend using Voltarra brand Silver Leaf for this tutorial.
